<article>
<div itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Article">
<div id="print_content"><h1 itemprop="name headline" style="margin-bottom:10px;">The Ayatollah, the Novelist [Salman Rushdie], and the West</h1>

<p class="sans-serif" style="margin:10px 0 0 0;"><b>
by Daniel Pipes<br />
<i>Commentary</i> <br />
<time class="nocontent" datetime="1989-06-00T00:00:00" itemprop="datePublished">June 1989</time></b></p>

<p class="no_screen sans-serif" style="margin:0 0 10px 0;"><b>http://www.danielpipes.org/186/the-ayatollah-the-novelist-and-the-west</b></p>

</div>

